        <div class="verdict">⭐ Rating: 4.2/5 — Best field coordination tool for construction teams</div>

        <p>Fieldwire was acquired by Hilti in 2021 for $300 million — a signal of how seriously the construction tools giant takes software. Since the acquisition, Fieldwire has maintained its independent product identity while benefiting from Hilti's resources and global distribution.</p>

        <p>The key thing to understand about Fieldwire: it's a <em>field management</em> tool, not a full project management platform. It doesn't handle budgets, invoicing, or change orders. What it does — plan management, task coordination, punch lists, and field communication — it does better than most.</p>

